{
  "stem": "6159.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Magda Hedges.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hedges is H-E-D-G-E-S.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mittler, M-I-T-T-L-E-R.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Margaret I am using in Australia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when we came, I found it's very hard for people to say Magda.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was an unusual name then, 44 years ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, yes, first names, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my husband born Heimann, H-E-I-M-A-N-N.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then he chose a name for escaping from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was Hegyeshalmi, which is a very hard name to spell.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You want me to spell it as well?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "H-E-G-Y-E-S-H-A-L-M-I.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we arrived to this country with that name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And soon I was ever asking for changing the names.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First we got Heges, actually, which is a H-E-G-E-S.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After naturalization, we could be Hedges and a proper English name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there are lots of name changes in my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "10Th of May, 1921.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "74.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Budapest, Hungary.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Growing up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, in the first 12 years of my life, was quite pleasant and easy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Except that my father had the occupation, which was a night occupation mostly, because he was in the restaurant business.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came home at night and got up mid-day, about.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember as sort of afraid of him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we never had much in common.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never had time to talk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother was the one who was-- not really spoiling me, but gave me everything what was possible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But when I was 12 years old, my father left my mother, after 30 years of marriage.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because I had three sisters, one brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was born after 10 years of my sister, of my last sister actually.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With me, three daughters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two sisters.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, three sisters, but one of them was a twin, died right after birth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I didn't even know her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just heard of her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the brother was the oldest.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
